Cam started talking trash.

795
00:33:34.293 --> 00:33:36.104
What the hell happened that day?

796
00:33:36.128 --> 00:33:38.197
<i>♪ ♪</i>

797
00:33:44.034 --> 00:33:45.810
[CREAKING. CLANGING]

798
00:33:48.165 --> 00:33:49.708
Fresh ice.

799
00:33:51.368 --> 00:33:52.948
Are you booking me yet?

800
00:33:53.598 --> 00:33:56.658
- Nope.
- Why?

801
00:33:56.682 --> 00:33:58.727
I don't know how many more
times I can confess.

802
00:33:58.751 --> 00:34:00.528
About three months ago. Malik and Iyana

803
00:34:00.552 --> 00:34:03.066
began interacting on Instagram.

804
00:34:03.514 --> 00:34:06.159
And eventually. they met up in person.

805
00:34:06.183 --> 00:34:11.339
The day after they met up.
Iyana went to a medical clinic.

806
00:34:11.363 --> 00:34:13.475
<i>and she got treated for injuries</i>

807
00:34:13.499 --> 00:34:15.704
<i>consistent with sexual assault.</i>

808
00:34:16.663 --> 00:34:18.371
<i>Now. the medical clinic
was obligated</i>

809
00:34:18.395 --> 00:34:20.667
<i>to report the injuries.
but they didn't.</i>

810
00:34:21.073 --> 00:34:23.879
So I spoke to the doctor
that treated her.

811
00:34:24.810 --> 00:34:27.466
and she said that Iyana insisted.

812
00:34:28.347 --> 00:34:30.358
<i>She said she got
in a fight with a friend.</i>

813
00:34:30.382 --> 00:34:32.794
<i>and she begged them not to tell.</i>

814
00:34:32.818 --> 00:34:34.295
<i>[SOMBER MUSIC]</i>

815
00:34:34.319 --> 00:34:37.899
The next night. you posted
a story threatening Malik.

816
00:34:37.923 --> 00:34:41.287
That's right. I did.

817
00:34:42.161 --> 00:34:43.563
I threatened him.

818
00:34:43.587 --> 00:34:45.306
And I was the one that shot him.

819
00:34:45.330 --> 00:34:46.741
So don't bring my sister into this.

820
00:34:46.765 --> 00:34:49.244
We traced the gun
that was used to kill Malik.

821
00:34:49.268 --> 00:34:51.312
The last Gangster Prophet that sold it.

822
00:34:51.336 --> 00:34:53.615
he confirmed he sold it to Iyana.

823
00:34:53.639 --> 00:34:55.408
She bought it for me!

824
00:34:55.432 --> 00:34:59.988
Cam. we found gloves
and a jacket in her locker.

825
00:35:00.012 --> 00:35:02.364
<i>It tested positive
for gunshot residue.</i>

826
00:35:04.349 --> 00:35:06.368
We have evidence.

827
00:35:08.320 --> 00:35:13.041
I... I should have
taken care of it myself.

828
00:35:15.360 --> 00:35:17.806
She told me what happened. and I...

829
00:35:17.830 --> 00:35:19.935
didn't know what to do.

830
00:35:20.791 --> 00:35:22.646
I went online.

831
00:35:23.769 --> 00:35:25.387
I threatened Malik.

832
00:35:27.139 --> 00:35:29.384
But I... I should have done more.

833
00:35:29.408 --> 00:35:31.786
He kept saying things back.

834
00:35:31.810 --> 00:35:33.788
I should have known she would...

835
00:35:33.812 --> 00:35:35.450
I get it.

836
00:35:39.496 --> 00:35:41.289
Then. please...

837
00:35:42.087 --> 00:35:46.025
please let me take the time.

838
00:35:46.049 --> 00:35:47.694
- I can't do that.
- Yes. you can.

839
00:35:47.718 --> 00:35:49.562
Have the evidence disappear. right?

840
00:35:49.586 --> 00:35:52.414
Say... say it was me.
She bought the gun for me.

841
00:35:53.398 --> 00:35:54.909
Look. I can do the time. She can't.

842
00:35:54.933 --> 00:35:56.811
She ain't strong like that.

843
00:35:56.835 --> 00:35:58.538
The jury will go easy on her.

844
00:35:58.562 --> 00:35:59.981
and she won't be tried as an adult.

845
00:36:00.005 --> 00:36:01.716
Juvie's just as bad!

846
00:36:01.740 --> 00:36:04.477
Let me do the time.
She's the victim here!

847
00:36:04.501 --> 00:36:06.136
Do you get that?

848
00:36:08.280 --> 00:36:09.290
She took a life.

849
00:36:09.314 --> 00:36:10.758
He took from her!

850
00:36:10.782 --> 00:36:12.351
I know.

851
00:36:14.244 --> 00:36:15.824
I know.

852
00:36:16.755 --> 00:36:18.660
Then help me.

853
00:36:19.116 --> 00:36:21.538
We can end this the right way.

854
00:36:21.960 --> 00:36:26.274
[CRYING] Just let me save
my little baby sister. please.

855
00:36:26.298 --> 00:36:27.433
Please.

856
00:36:27.457 --> 00:36:31.646
I will help Iyana as much as I can.

857
00:36:31.670 --> 00:36:33.288
I promise you that.

858
00:36:36.052 --> 00:36:38.620
But that's the best that I can do.

859
00:36:38.644 --> 00:36:45.660
<i>♪ ♪</i>

860
00:36:45.684 --> 00:36:47.052
I'm sorry.

861
00:36:53.283 --> 00:36:56.037
More police? This can't be legal.

862
00:36:56.061 --> 00:36:58.006
You can't just sit here
and not tell us anything.

863
00:36:58.030 --> 00:36:59.274
It's lawful detainment. sir.

864
00:36:59.298 --> 00:37:00.742
Nah. you can't just hold us here.

865
00:37:00.766 --> 00:37:02.310
My daughter needs to go to school.

866
00:37:02.334 --> 00:37:04.037
We have work. We have rights. man.

867
00:37:04.061 --> 00:37:06.114
Please tell us you're here
to stop this nonsense

868
00:37:06.138 --> 00:37:07.106
and let this child go to school.

869
00:37:07.130 --> 00:37:08.483
Iyana. I'm Officer Torres.

870
00:37:08.507 --> 00:37:10.551
I'm here to arrest you
for the murder of Malik Hunter.

871
00:37:10.575 --> 00:37:11.644
I need you to stand up

872
00:37:11.668 --> 00:37:12.712
and place your hands behind your back.

873
00:37:12.736 --> 00:37:14.322
- What? What?
- No. no. stop.

874
00:37:14.346 --> 00:37:15.790
- Gerald... Gerald.
- What's going on?

875
00:37:15.814 --> 00:37:17.602
- Stop. What are you doing?
- Iyana...

876
00:37:17.626 --> 00:37:18.925
- What? No. we need our lawyer.
- What's happening?

877
00:37:18.949 --> 00:37:20.662
- Daddy...
- The lawyer is on his way.

878
00:37:20.686 --> 00:37:22.030
Right now. I need you to stand up

879
00:37:22.054 --> 00:37:23.364
and place your hands behind your back.

880
00:37:23.388 --> 00:37:24.559
Get away from her!

881
00:37:24.583 --> 00:37:26.025
Iyana. look at me.

882
00:37:26.049 --> 00:37:28.561
We're going to do this
one thing at a time. okay?

883
00:37:28.585 --> 00:37:30.004
Can you do that for me?

884
00:37:30.028 --> 00:37:31.339
Stand up.

885
00:37:31.363 --> 00:37:37.045
<i>♪ ♪</i>

886
00:37:37.530 --> 00:37:39.339
Now. just give me your hands.

887
00:37:39.363 --> 00:37:40.564
Hold them up for me.

888
00:37:49.881 --> 00:37:51.084
- What's happening?
- Stop.

889
00:37:51.108 --> 00:37:52.794
Why are they putting cuffs on my baby?

890
00:37:52.818 --> 00:37:54.095
What happened?

891
00:37:54.119 --> 00:37:56.230
They're gonna... we're gonna be
right behind you.

892
00:37:56.254 --> 00:37:58.257
- It's okay.
- Where are they taking her?

893
00:37:58.281 --> 00:37:59.400
Where are you taking her?

894
00:37:59.424 --> 00:38:01.235
[SOBBING] Can we come. please?

895
00:38:01.259 --> 00:38:02.870
Baby. don't worry!

896
00:38:02.894 --> 00:38:08.276
<i>♪ ♪</i>

897
00:38:08.300 --> 00:38:11.970
Okay. now can you turn
to the other side. please?

898
00:38:14.373 --> 00:38:15.775
Iyana?

899
00:38:15.799 --> 00:38:17.552
Could you turn
to the other side. please?

900
00:38:17.576 --> 00:38:23.925
<i>♪ ♪</i>

901
00:38:23.949 --> 00:38:25.495
Now face the front.

902
00:38:28.387 --> 00:38:30.458
Hey. it's okay.

903
00:38:31.156 --> 00:38:34.235
Iyana. could you look up for me. please?

904
00:38:34.259 --> 00:38:41.249
<i>♪ ♪</i>

905
00:38:45.671 --> 00:38:47.215
All right.

906
00:38:47.239 --> 00:38:50.985
We can wait here until they arrive.

907
00:38:51.009 --> 00:38:52.587
Have a seat.

908
00:38:52.611 --> 00:38:54.065
Are your hands hurting you?

909
00:38:56.748 --> 00:38:57.808
Here.

910
00:39:13.364 --> 00:39:15.600
What's gonna happen to me?

911
00:39:21.306 --> 00:39:23.034
When you get inside.

912
00:39:24.429 --> 00:39:26.931
you keep your head down.

913
00:39:27.446 --> 00:39:28.589
Okay?

914
00:39:28.613 --> 00:39:30.958
You try not to draw eyes on you.

915
00:39:30.982 --> 00:39:33.062
You understand what I mean?

916
00:39:34.586 --> 00:39:37.665
You listen to the correction
officers who are nice.

917
00:39:37.689 --> 00:39:40.403
and you stay far away from the rest.

918
00:39:41.393 --> 00:39:45.283
You don't fight. ever.

919
00:39:46.732 --> 00:39:50.079
And if you have a problem.
you contact your lawyer.

920
00:39:51.670 --> 00:39:53.500
or you contact me.

921
00:39:53.525 --> 00:39:56.896
<i>♪ ♪</i>

922
00:39:57.400 --> 00:39:58.820
You got that?

923
00:39:58.844 --> 00:40:05.876
<i>♪ ♪</i>

924
00:41:29.125 --> 00:41:32.128
[WOLF HOWLS]

925
00:41:35.073 --> 00:41:38.085
<i>[DRAMATIC MUSIC]</i>

926
00:41:38.109 --> 00:41:45.141
<i>♪ ♪</i>

926
